{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-goanimes-api",
    "name": "GoAnimes",
    "description": "GoAnimes — admin API + URLs do addon Stremio.\n\n**Variáveis de coleção:** `baseUrl`, `adminApiKey`, `rssSourceId`, `sampleRssUrl`, `seriesId`, `videoId`, `goaiAuditLimit`, `goaiAuditOffset`, `goaiAuditConfidenceMin`, `goaiAuditConfidenceMax`, `goaiSeriesId`\n\n- **Meta / Stream (path):** coloca em `seriesId` e `videoId` o id **já com encoding URL** (ex. `goanimes%3Aseries%3A…`, `goanimes%3Avid%3A…`), ou edita o path manualmente no Postman.\n- **Inspect series:** usa `seriesId` **sem** encoding no query param; o Postman codifica no `?id=`.\n- **GoAI audit:** `goaiSeriesId` é o `series_id` do catálogo (igual ao retornado em **List series audits**). O script desse GET pode preencher `goaiSeriesId` automaticamente a partir do primeiro item.\n\nSe **não** usares `GOANIMES_ADMIN_API_KEY`, na pasta **Admin** → **Authorization** → **No Auth**.\n\n**Create RSS source** grava `rssSourceId` para o **Delete**.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8080" },
    { "key": "adminApiKey", "value": "" },
    { "key": "rssSourceId", "value": "" },
    {
      "key": "sampleRssUrl",
      "value": "https://www.erai-raws.info/feed/?type=torrent&token=SEU_TOKEN_AQUI"
    },
    { "key": "seriesId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "videoId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "goaiAuditLimit", "value": "50" },
    { "key": "goaiAuditOffset", "value": "0" },
    { "key": "goaiAuditConfidenceMin", "value": "" },
    { "key": "goaiAuditConfidenceMax", "value": "" },
    { "key": "goaiSeriesId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Public (Stremio / health)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Manifest (addon Stremio)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/manifest.json"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Catalog anime / goanimes",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/catalog/anime/goanimes.json"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Catalog · Últimos 7 dias",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/catalog/anime/goanimes-week.json",
            "description": "Só séries com pelo menos um episódio com data Released nos últimos 7 dias (UTC)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Catalog · goanimes + genre extra",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/catalog/anime/goanimes/genre=Fantasia.json",
            "description": "Igual ao Stremio com filtro de género (labels em pt-BR do manifest)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Meta (anime / series id)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/meta/anime/{{seriesId}}.json",
            "description": "Define `seriesId` com id path-encoded (`:` → `%3A`), ou substitui no URL."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Meta (series / series id)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/meta/series/{{seriesId}}.json",
            "description": "Mesmo conteúdo que anime em muitos clientes; útil para testar o tipo `series`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Stream (anime / video id)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/stream/anime/{{videoId}}.json",
            "description": "`videoId` = id `goanimes:vid:…` (encoded no path)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Stream (series / video id)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/stream/series/{{videoId}}.json",
            "description": "Alternativa com tipo `series` no path."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [
          {
            "key": "token",
            "value": "{{adminApiKey}}",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "RSS sources",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Create RSS source",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                      "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                      "  if (j && j.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('rssSourceId', j.id);",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"url\": \"{{sampleRssUrl}}\",\n  \"label\": \"Erai\"\n}"
                },
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rss-sources"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "List RSS sources",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rss-sources"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "Delete RSS source",
              "request": {
                "method": "DELETE",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rss-sources/{{rssSourceId}}"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Sync",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Rebuild (sync now)",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/rebuild"
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "Sync status",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/sync-status",
                "description": "Inclui `errors`: linhas de falha do último sync (RSS, save, enrich), persistidas no snapshot."
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Inspect",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Inspect catalog",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inspect/catalog",
                "description": "Resumo de todas as séries + enrichment (validação / QA)."
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "Inspect series",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inspect/series?id={{seriesId}}",
                "description": "Query `id` = série Stremio (ex. goanimes:series:…). Podes colar com `:`; o cliente codifica no query string."
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "GoAI audit",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "List series audits",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                      "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                      "  if (j && Array.isArray(j.items) && j.items.length > 0 && j.items[0].series_id) {",
                      "    pm.collectionVariables.set('goaiSeriesId', j.items[0].series_id);",
                      "  }",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/goai-audit/series?limit={{goaiAuditLimit}}&offset={{goaiAuditOffset}}&confidence_min={{goaiAuditConfidenceMin}}&confidence_max={{goaiAuditConfidenceMax}}",
                "description": "Lista séries com linha em `goai_series_audit` (paginação `limit` / `offset`). Filtros opcionais: `confidence_min` e `confidence_max` (0..1).\n\n**503** se o repositório GoAI não estiver configurado. Após **200**, o teste grava `goaiSeriesId` com o primeiro `series_id` da página (útil para **Re-audit**)."
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "Re-audit series (full — apaga release audits)",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [],
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/goai-audit/series/{{goaiSeriesId}}/reaudit",
                "description": "Corpo vazio ou `scope` omitido / `full` / `default`: apaga `goai_release_audit` desta série e marca `needs_reaudit`.\n\n**404** se ainda não existir linha em `goai_series_audit` para esse id."
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "Re-audit series (series_only — só flag)",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"scope\": \"series_only\"\n}"
                },
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/goai-audit/series/{{goaiSeriesId}}/reaudit",
                "description": "`scope`: `series_only` ou `flag_only` — só `SetSeriesNeedsReaudit`, mantém linhas em `goai_release_audit`."
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
